snippet.title: SteamWorld Quest - Official Trailer - Out Now on Nintendo Switch, PC, iOS/iPadOS and Stadia!
snippet.description:
Triumph over evil with the hand you're dealt in SteamWorld Quest: Hand of Gilgamech! Out now on Nintendo Switch, Stadia and PC (Steam, GOG) for $24.99 / €24.99 as well as iOS/iPadOS for $9.99 / €9.99! ⚔️🃏🤖  #SWQuest #NintendoSwitch
